Aturan baru penalti dari FIFA ini akan mengubah sepakbola selamanya ğŸ˜³
description:
Inilah aturan penalti baru yang akan mengubah sepak bola selamanya.
FIFA baru saja memutuskan untuk mengubah aturan penalti lagi â€” dan ini sudah kedua kalinya dalam 2 tahun terakhir.
Sekarang, mencetak gol akan jadi jauh lebih sulit.
Setelah Piala Dunia 2022, FIFA sempat memperkenalkan aturan baru soal batas gerakan kiper sebelum tendangan dilakukan.
Emiliano MartÃ­nez sering mengganggu penendang lawan, bahkan melempar bola menjauh di final sehingga TchouamÃ©ni gagal menendang.
Sejak saat itu, FIFA menambahkan aturan bahwa kalau kiper bergerak keluar garis sebelum bola ditendang, dia akan mendapat kartu kuning.
Namun sekarang, FIFA ingin sedikit mempermudah tugas kiper.
Ini bukan ide â€œWingangerâ€ di mana penendang berhadapan satu lawan satu dengan kiper,
tapi perubahan ini tetap besar pengaruhnya.
Aturan baru ini berhubungan dengan rebound setelah penalti.
Biasanya, kalau kiper berhasil menepis bola, penyerang langsung bisa menyambar bola muntah.
Tapi di bawah aturan baru, bola akan dianggap mati setelah kiper melakukan penyelamatan.
Artinya, tidak ada lagi rebound, dan permainan akan dimulai ulang dengan tendangan gawang.

title: The Entire Outlast Timeline To Fall Asleep To
description:
Welcome back. Tonight, we drift slowly into the complete and unbroken chronicle of Outlast â€” a tale of science masquerading as salvation, of the Murkoff Corporationâ€™s pursuit of control that turned the human mind into its own executioner. This isnâ€™t just a horror timeline. Itâ€™s a historical autopsy â€” from 1918 Germanyâ€™s experimental labs, to Cold War deserts, to the decaying halls of Mount Massive and the wave-distorted wastelands of Temple Gate. Every document, every scar, every whispered name connects here â€” Wernicke, Coyle, Knoth, Hope, Park â€” stitched together into one soft, continuous descent.

Youâ€™ll hear how a single scientistâ€™s wartime visions became the blueprint for programmable charisma, how the Morphogenic Engine birthed the Walrider swarm, and how belief itself was weaponized through waves, lesions, and guilt. Weâ€™ll move through CIA black budgets, Sinaloaâ€™s reagent trials, MKUltraâ€™s hypnosis wards, the rise of Temple Gateâ€™s cult, and the lingering hum that outlived them all.

So, as you listen, let the quiet unraveling of this story ease you into rest â€” a slow immersion into the machinery of madness, where control and chaos sleep side by side.

â¸»

 â€¢ The origins of Dr. Rudolph Wernicke and Murkoffâ€™s postwar rise under Project Paperclip

 â€¢ Sullivan Knothâ€™s prophetic delusions and the formation of Temple Gate
 â€¢ The events of Outlast 1 and Whistleblower â€” Miles Upshur, Waylon Park, and Billy Hopeâ€™s ascension

 â€¢ The aftermath explored in The Murkoff Account, Project Lupara, and the modern trials

ğŸ”¥ The Trial Was to Outlast the Winter â€” The Human Built Stone Ovens and Fed the Camp Warm Meals | HFY Story

On the frozen world of Kelvara-9, the galaxyâ€™s elite cadets face the toughest military survival challenge ever designed â€” six weeks in deadly winter, with nothing but basic supplies and their instincts. Most are built for the cold. One isnâ€™t.

Marcus Webb, a lone human, arrives with no special tech, no enhanced biology, and no chance... or so everyone thinks.

Instead of freezing, he builds stone ovens, bakes bread from scratch, and turns a cutthroat survival trial into a thriving, cooperative camp. While others huddle in silence, Marcus shares warmth, food, and something alien cadets have never seen before: community in the cold.

This story flips the script on traditional sci-fi trials, showing how humanityâ€™s oldest survival strategies â€” cooperation, cooking, and creativity â€” can outmatch raw strength and isolation.

title: Indonesia Coach bus driving | Euro bus simulator 2025 Android gameplay #game 1 Part 76
description:
Indonesian Bus Simulator Game with the latest features Part 76

This game of Indonesia Bus Simulator will make you feel like a real bus driver when you play it. Coupled with the quality of the graphics which are very pleasing to the eye, the combination of sharp and realistic colors will make you more comfortable to playing this game. The route your bus takes to get to the destination city is almost exactly the same as the original road. Supported by realistic traffic conditions and you can choose the crowd level, this game never gets boring to keep playing!

And in this game, you can choose the steering wheel mode according to your wishes! There is a right-left button mode, there is a gadget shake model, and there is also a steering wheel mode like the original! This game is also equipped with various cool features. Equipped with an automatic open-close door button, 3D horn sound, turn signal lights, hazard lights, wipers, hand brakes, high beam lights and several camera modes. You also don't need to worry about getting lost when heading to your destination city because there is a map feature to guide you!

In this game you can also measure your success in playing this game by the amount of money you can collect. You can earn this money from your work delivering passengers to destination cities. But you don't have to spend the money you have earned just to buy fuel, because in this game you don't need to refill your bus with fuel. From the money you collect, you can buy another bus. In total there are 2 types of buses that you can use, and both are double cabin buses or double-decker buses. Of course, this is a very exciting mission to undertake in order to have the bus of your dreams!

So what are you waiting for! There is no reason for you to not downloaded this game immediately. Hurry up and drive your bus, and go to your destination city so you can have lots of money. And feel the real excitement by becoming a real bus driver!

title: Indonesia Coach bus driving | Euro bus simulator 2025 Android gameplay #game 1 Part 86
description:
Indonesian Bus Simulator Game with the latest features Part 86

This game of Indonesia Bus Simulator will make you feel like a real bus driver when you play it. Coupled with the quality of the graphics which are very pleasing to the eye, the combination of sharp and realistic colors will make you more comfortable to playing this game. The route your bus takes to get to the destination city is almost exactly the same as the original road. Supported by realistic traffic conditions and you can choose the crowd level, this game never gets boring to keep playing!

And in this game, you can choose the steering wheel mode according to your wishes! There is a right-left button mode, there is a gadget shake model, and there is also a steering wheel mode like the original! This game is also equipped with various cool features. Equipped with an automatic open-close door button, 3D horn sound, turn signal lights, hazard lights, wipers, hand brakes, high beam lights and several camera modes. You also don't need to worry about getting lost when heading to your destination city because there is a map feature to guide you!

In this game you can also measure your success in playing this game by the amount of money you can collect. You can earn this money from your work delivering passengers to destination cities. But you don't have to spend the money you have earned just to buy fuel, because in this game you don't need to refill your bus with fuel. From the money you collect, you can buy another bus. In total there are 2 types of buses that you can use, and both are double cabin buses or double-decker buses. Of course, this is a very exciting mission to undertake in order to have the bus of your dreams!

So what are you waiting for! There is no reason for you to not downloaded this game immediately. Hurry up and drive your bus, and go to your destination city so you can have lots of money. And feel the real excitement by becoming a real bus driver!

title: Cuando AGE OF EMPIRES se vuelve RPG âš”ï¸ #gaming
Indonesia Coach bus driving | Euro bus simulator 2025 Android gameplay #game 1 Part 79
description:
Indonesian Bus Simulator Game with the latest features Part 79

This game of Indonesia Bus Simulator will make you feel like a real bus driver when you play it. Coupled with the quality of the graphics which are very pleasing to the eye, the combination of sharp and realistic colors will make you more comfortable to playing this game. The route your bus takes to get to the destination city is almost exactly the same as the original road. Supported by realistic traffic conditions and you can choose the crowd level, this game never gets boring to keep playing!

And in this game, you can choose the steering wheel mode according to your wishes! There is a right-left button mode, there is a gadget shake model, and there is also a steering wheel mode like the original! This game is also equipped with various cool features. Equipped with an automatic open-close door button, 3D horn sound, turn signal lights, hazard lights, wipers, hand brakes, high beam lights and several camera modes. You also don't need to worry about getting lost when heading to your destination city because there is a map feature to guide you!

In this game you can also measure your success in playing this game by the amount of money you can collect. You can earn this money from your work delivering passengers to destination cities. But you don't have to spend the money you have earned just to buy fuel, because in this game you don't need to refill your bus with fuel. From the money you collect, you can buy another bus. In total there are 2 types of buses that you can use, and both are double cabin buses or double-decker buses. Of course, this is a very exciting mission to undertake in order to have the bus of your dreams!

So what are you waiting for! There is no reason for you to not downloaded this game immediately. Hurry up and drive your bus, and go to your destination city so you can have lots of money. And feel the real excitement by becoming a real bus driver!
